'''ExcelStar''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] manufacturing corporation. They were closely related to [[Sienar Fleet Systems/Legends|Sienar Fleet Systems]], modifying their starships for the public.

==Description==
'''ExcelStar''' [[Starship/Legends|starship]] construction corporation often modified Seinar Fleet Systems craft for personal usage by non-military pilots.

